OL,3,CGovernment health group took months to
OL,4,Cshare news of 'high risk' breach
OL,6,FGuernsey's Health and Social Care
OL,7,FCommittee (HSC) has been reprimanded
OL,8,Fby the island's Data Protection
OL,9,FAuthority after significant delays in
OL,10,Freporting a "high risk" personal data
OL,11,Fbreach.
OL,13,FAn investigation found that sensitive
OL,14,Finformation about three people,
OL,15,Fincluding substance misuse, was
OL,16,Finappropriately shared in December
OL,17,F2023.
