OL,3,CGovernment health group took months to
OL,4,Cshare news of 'high risk' breach
OL,6,FIt took HSC 52 days to tell the
OL,7,Fregulator - the law requires them to
OL,8,Fbe notified within 72 hours - and
OL,9,Fbetween 50 and 62 days to inform the
OL,10,Findividuals whose data had been
OL,11,Fbreached.
OL,13,FHSC says it needed longer than the 72-
OL,14,Fhour window to understand the extent
OL,15,Fof the data breach but the regulator
OL,16,Fbelieves this was not a valid reason
OL,17,Fto delay notifying them.
