OL,4,Cshare news of 'high risk' breach
OL,6,FThe group should also have written to
OL,7,Fthose affected "as soon as it was
OL,8,Fpractical", something the regulator
OL,9,Fsays it did not do.
OL,11,FHSC says it needed to check contact
OL,12,Fdetails for two of the people before
OL,13,Fsending letters but the regulator
OL,14,Fconcluded this was not done in a
OL,15,Ftimely manner as required under the
OL,16,Flaw.
